»CL8:Did you know...
»CL1:The Shut Down command on the Start
menu enables you to safely shut down
your computer.

»CL8:Did you know...
»CL3:You can use long filenames when you
save documents. You can even use
spaces!

»CL8:Did you know...
»CL7:You can minimize neck strain by








positioning your monitor at eye level.

»CL8:Did you know...
»CL1:You can solve memory problems on your
computer by using the Memory Trouble-
shooter in Help.

»CL8:Did you know...
»CL5:You can solve memory problems by
deleting Windows from your harddisk
(Not an official tip, but it »CL4:really
works»:-)).


